Revision history for Perl module Module::InstalledVersion

0.05_01 2014-06-02 NEILB
    - The result now includes the full path to the module. RT#79217
    - The testsuite would fail if you had developer releases (with an _ in
      the version) of any of CPAN, Fcntl, or Text::Wrap installed. RT#38740
    - Added other modules for getting version to SEE ALSO
    - Switched to Dist::Zilla
    - Added github repo to pod
    - Reformatted this file as per CPAN::Changes::Spec

0.05 2001-10-09 SKUD
    - Thanks to a patch from Jos Boumans, now picks up versions 
      in the form $Foo::Bar::VERSION

0.04 2001-09-20 SKUD
    - One-line change to modversion so it doesn't barf if the 
      module isn't installed

0.03 2001-09-14 SKUD
    - Now uses File::Spec for platform independence
      (patch provided by Ville Skyttä <ville.skytta@iki.fi>)
    - Included a script, "modversion", to easily find a module's version.
    - Now sets $m->{dir} even if it can't find a version.

0.02 2001-09-10 SKUD
    - Removed an unnecessary debugging "print"

0.01 2001-09-10 SKUD
    - Original version
